  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cat & Farm Pals is a fun match game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match the same animals to get points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match more animals for a higher score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete on leaderboards to win trophies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Match and Win!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match the same animals to create new ones. Earn points for each combination!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/316c1baeb2b2cbdc6c4f888fce5f144a.poster.avif?t=1772095922\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/316c1baeb2b2cbdc6c4f888fce5f144a.webm?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/316c1baeb2b2cbdc6c4f888fce5f144a.mp4?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Trophies, Be a Leader!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with friends or global players to climb the rankings and win trophies! Join weekly and monthly competitions to secure your spot on the leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d211f2b24a582b5e84d865661beb28d7.poster.avif?t=1772095922\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d211f2b24a582b5e84d865661beb28d7.webm?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d211f2b24a582b5e84d865661beb28d7.mp4?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control the area, don't lose!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merging animals can move others, so watch the area! If an animal goes out of bounds, you lose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d7bad7cae946c2d67f7f884fedb7c205.poster.avif?t=1772095922\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d7bad7cae946c2d67f7f884fedb7c205.webm?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d7bad7cae946c2d67f7f884fedb7c205.mp4?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cat & Farm Pals is a fun match game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match the same animals to get points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match more animals for a higher score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete on leaderboards to win trophies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Match and Win!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match the same animals to create new ones. Earn points for each combination!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/316c1baeb2b2cbdc6c4f888fce5f144a.poster.avif?t=1772095922\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/316c1baeb2b2cbdc6c4f888fce5f144a.webm?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/316c1baeb2b2cbdc6c4f888fce5f144a.mp4?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Trophies, Be a Leader!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with friends or global players to climb the rankings and win trophies! Join weekly and monthly competitions to secure your spot on the leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d211f2b24a582b5e84d865661beb28d7.poster.avif?t=1772095922\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d211f2b24a582b5e84d865661beb28d7.webm?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d211f2b24a582b5e84d865661beb28d7.mp4?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control the area, don't lose!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merging animals can move others, so watch the area! If an animal goes out of bounds, you lose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d7bad7cae946c2d67f7f884fedb7c205.poster.avif?t=1772095922\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d7bad7cae946c2d67f7f884fedb7c205.webm?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d7bad7cae946c2d67f7f884fedb7c205.mp4?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
